<P>
SRI LANKAN TROOPS KILL 19 TAMIL REBELS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
COLOMBO, Sri Lanka 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Sri Lankan forces killed 19 Tamil rebels in the north and east, military 
sources said Friday. 
</P>
<P>
Rebels, fighting for a separate homeland for Sri Lanka's Tamil minority, killed 
21 members of the Sinhalese majority community and 21 Muslims in a 10-day 
period. 
</P>
