<TEXT>
<P>
As far as the rest of the country is concerned Orange County is nothing, nil, 
zero, zilch. 
</P>
<P>
Plain and simple it does not exist. This country revolves around two cities: 
New York and L.A. Sorry, but that's the way it is. 
</P>
<P>
If one can put up with a sea of provincial mental midgets, Orange County is a 
pleasant place to live. 
</P>
<P>
ROBERT HUNT 
