by Colette Malouf, at Fred Segal, Santa Monica. Silver, glass-bead and marble 
hair pin by Diane Komater, $80, at Wilder Place, Melrose. Silver "Ellipse" hair 
pin, $175, and silver "Target" hair pin, $165, by Lisa Jenks LTD,at Wilder 
Place. Acrylic and gold-leaf hair stick, $200, by Dana Schneider, at Wilder 
