<HEADLINE>
<P>
HOW TO PREVENT CHILD DROWNINGS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I have something to tell the crusaders for "Safe Pools": You can't legislate 
against stupidity! 
</P>
<P>
Leaving your child alone by a pool for even three seconds is just plain stupid. 
No law, fence, or alarm will help you. 
</P>
<P>
If you are careless enough to leave your child alone by a pool without a fence, 
you will be careless enough to leave your child alone by a pool with a fence. 
</P>
<P>
It is sad that the children pay the price for their parents' lack of care. 
</P>
<P>
MICHAEL T. LESTER 
</P>
