path in Culver City. One rider was killed on the trail. At least seven attacks 
have occurred on the path in the last four months.; Photo, Barbara (Bobbi) 
Gold, Culver City bike-path safety coordinator, says much bike path crime is 
unreported. GARY FRIEDMAN / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Last summer Bill Evans 
was robbed of his bike at knifepoint on the Los Angeles River path. MINDY 
