<P>
HUNTINGTON PARK BEGINS YEARLONG CLEANUP DRIVE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
HUNTINGTON PARK 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
This month the city's Chamber of Commerce will begin its Clean Up Huntington 
Park campaign, a yearlong effort. 
</P>
<P>
The chamber, together with service clubs and businesses, will be providing more 
street trash cans. Each month the chamber will present certificates of 
recognition to contributing businesses. 
</P>
<P>
The chamber is asking businesses to refrain from distributing leaflets or ads 
on sidewalks or in store lobbies and to pick up litter in front of and around 
their business. 
</P>
