AMERICAN BOWL (FOOTBALL GAME); LONDON (ENGLAND); SPORTS FRANCHISES; WORLD 
LEAGUE OF AMERICAN FOOTBALL 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA080590-0188 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 257613 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
August 5, 1990, Sunday, Bulldog Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
