baseball tips with the Dutch junior national team during a tour of the country 
this month. IRFAN KHAN / for The Times; Photo, Mitch Miller's team will be 
playing to win but the junior high teacher concedes his players have other 
goals as well. "It's an educational experience," he says. IRFAN KHAN / for The 
Times 
</P>
